OL,3,CRescuers focus on alternative shaft to
OL,4,Creach missing men in flooded Laos cave
OL,6,FRescuers are searching for an
OL,7,Falternative vertical shaft as they
OL,8,Frace against time to reach two men
OL,9,Ftrapped for nearly a fortnight inside
OL,10,Fa flooded cave in Laos.
OL,12,FFive of the seven people initially
OL,13,Fmissing have been rescued in a
OL,14,Fmountainous area of central Xaisomboun
OL,15,Fprovince.
OL,17,FThe villagers entered the narrow
OL,18,Ftunnels on May 20 in search of gold,
OL,19,Fbut heavy rainfall flooded the main
OL,20,Fentrance, making it impassable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
