OL,3,CRescuers focus on alternative shaft to
OL,4,Creach missing men in flooded Laos cave
OL,6,FA massive search and rescue operation
OL,7,Fbegan last month, about 120 kilometres
OL,8,F(75 miles) north of the capital,
OL,9,FVientiane.
OL,11,FMalaysian diver Lee Kian Lie, who is
OL,12,Finvolved, said workers were pumping
OL,13,Fwater out of the cave.
OL,15,F"We will go into the suspected area to
OL,16,Fcontinue the search if the water level
OL,17,Fis lowered," he told the Associated
OL,18,FPress.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@LO]
