OL,3,CRescuers focus on alternative shaft to
OL,4,Creach missing men in flooded Laos cave
OL,6,FAnother team of rescuers is also
OL,7,Flooking around the other side of the
OL,8,Fcave in hopes of finding a dry passage
OL,9,Fthat could provide access to the area
OL,10,Fwhere the missing people are believed
OL,11,Fto be trapped, Mr Lie added.
OL,13,FRescue teams from Laos and
OL,14,Fneighbouring Thailand have been
OL,15,Fworking alongside divers from
OL,16,Fcountries including Finland, Malaysia,
OL,17,FJapan, Indonesia, France and Australia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
