OL,3,CRescuers focus on alternative shaft to
OL,4,Creach missing men in flooded Laos cave
OL,6,FLater on Sunday, Laos's Rescue
OL,7,FVolunteer for People group posted on
OL,8,FFacebook that search operations were
OL,9,Fsuspended due to heavy rain causing
OL,10,F"massive amounts of water" to flow
OL,11,Fdown into the area. They said efforts
OL,12,Fwould continue on Monday.
OL,14,FKengkaj Bongkawong, head of the Thai
OL,15,Fgroup Metta Tham Rescue Kalasin, said
OL,16,Fteams are also looking for air shafts
OL,17,Ffrom above that may provide access
OL,18,Finto the cave.
