OL,3,CRescuers focus on alternative shaft to
OL,4,Creach missing men in flooded Laos cave
OL,6,FVideo shows rescuers finding some of
OL,7,Fthe missing Laos villages who were
OL,8,Flost in the cave
OL,10,FHe told reporters: "The team and I
OL,11,Fhave used a radar scanner and
OL,12,Fsatellite images and many other things
OL,13,Fas a basis for our navigation of the
OL,14,Fmountain."
OL,16,FBut the expert warned that even if a
OL,17,Fsuitable alternative entrance is
OL,18,Ffound, "it's going to be a very tough
OL,19,Fjob," with access difficult and the
OL,20,Fconstant problem of continuing rain
OL,21,Fflooding the cave.
