OL,3,CRescuers focus on alternative shaft to
OL,4,Creach missing men in flooded Laos cave
OL,6,FBongkawong said it would require not
OL,7,Fonly pumping water out, but also
OL,8,Finstalling equipment to keep
OL,9,Fventilating the cave's air supply.
OL,11,FThe two missing men are trapped deeper
OL,12,Finside the cave than the location
OL,13,Fwhere the five survivors were
OL,14,Foriginally found on Wednesday. But the
OL,15,Fpassage into that area is said to be
OL,16,Fvery narrow and heavily flooded.
OL,18,FEarlier on Monday, it was reported
OL,19,Fknocking responses had been heard on
OL,20,Fat least two occasions in the last 24
OL,21,Fhours.
